WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.463 --> 00:00:06.924
[Coop grunting]

2
00:00:07.007 --> 00:00:08.967
[ominous music playing]

3
00:00:14.890 --> 00:00:16.725
[grunting continues]

4
00:00:16.808 --> 00:00:18.393
[footsteps approaching]

5
00:00:18.477 --> 00:00:20.854
[breathes heavily]

6
00:00:22.981 --> 00:00:24.274
