My arms got to hold you so ♪

324
00:19:05.312 --> 00:19:11.902
♪ My life will be in your keeping
Waking. sleeping. laughing. weeping ♪

325
00:19:11.985 --> 00:19:17.491
♪ Longer than always
Is a long. long. long time ♪

